<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-18 09:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3597 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l BC-SPCL-TRUCKS-MARKET-BO     11-18 1189
