<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-18 11:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3637 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-SPCL-TRUCKS-BUYING-BO     11-18 0999
