   COXNET BOOKS _ (EDS: This is the CoxNet Books page for the
current week. This layout is now available.)
</P>
<P>
   COXNET BOOKS 1116 -- Publishers are gearing up for the holiday
season with a large assortment of coffee-table publications.
(O'Briant, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes 3-column
