 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    KEEPING UP WITH THE FULANOS. The rise and fall of the Latin
America's middle class: After a decade of reform, would-be
consumers find pocketbooks woefully pinched.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-MIDDLE-CLASS-POOR-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
 &HT;    
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased _ the rate is not
