<P>
   &UR; LIFESTYLE &LR;   &UR; (l) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO-GAMES (Undated) _ Whatever you think of video games, don't
think of them as solely child's play. Fifty-four percent of the
primary users of console games like Sony's Playstation or Sega's
Dreamcast are 18 and over. By Nathan Cobb. 1500 words.
