<P>
   BBA-MVP-RODRIQUEZ (Undated) _ In an upset, Punch Rodriguez of
the Texas Rangers wins the American League mvp award, beating out
Pedro Martinez of the Red Sox. And the reason he did so is that two
writers _ apparently subscribing to the theory that pitchers should
not get mvp awards _ left Martinez completely off the ballot. By
Buster Olney.
</P>
<P>
   BKW-PREVIEW (Undated) _ Except for one charity doubleheader on
Sunday and the Preseason National Invitation Tournament, which
began on Monday, the women's college basketball season will begin
Friday night. The best teams figure to be such old reliables as
Connecticut, Tennessee, Louisiana Tech, Rutgers, Georgia and UCLA,
but beware of a dozen or so others waiting to drag a marquee team
down to earth. By Frank Litsky.
</P>
