   COXNET NASCAR 1119: AWESOME BILL'S POPULARITY : Our fearless
reporter uncovers facts on why Bill Elliott -- Awesome Bill from
Dawsonville -- wins NASCAR's Most Popular Driver award every year.
Simple: The good folks from Dawsonville. Ga., keep finding ways to
stuff the ballot box. In fact, NASCAR has changed the system four
times in an effort to prevent Elliott from dominating the vote. But
Dawsonville residents go to great lengths to find ways to make
their man, No. 1. And he'll probably win the award again this year.
