</P>
<P>
   FBC-FLA-FSU _ GAINESVILLE, Fla. _ Advancing Florida-Florida
State. The winner not only gets bragging rights, but will still be
very much in the hunt for the national championship. (Barnhart,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
