<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-18 18:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4227 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e BC-INTERVIEW-ANG-LEE-DEV     11-18 1299
