features recent finds by Heade; A Brittany jewel regains its
17th-century luster. (Moved).
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-Q&AMP;A (Undated) _ Question and answers on travel. This
week: Bird-watching in Rio; France's Picasso museums; Sicily-Malta
ferries. By Suzanne MacNeille. (Moved).
</P>
