<SLUG> BC-OBIT-BOWLES-ART-3TAKES(TRIMS)-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PAUL BOWLES, COMPOSER AND AUTHOR KNOWN FOR `SHELTERING SKY,' DIES
AT 88 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDS: A short version, OBIT-BOWLES-SHORT has also moved.)  
(ART ADV: Photos NYT12, NYT13 were sent to NYT photo clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling
888-603-1036 or 888-346-9867.) 
(js) 
