<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-18 21:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4474 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-BKW-PREVIEW-2TAKES-NY     11-18 1065
