</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-BONFIRE-COLLAPSE-NYT, which
moved in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``We're not sure what might be holding up what, and the crew has
to be meticulous at what they're doing. This is far worse than in a
building collapse in that the structure twisted as it collapsed and
all of the pieces are tangled together.''
</P>
<P>
   _DR. KEM BENNETT, during the rescue effort at Texas A&AMP;M
University.
